introduction: A man believed himself to be a playboy. He dates a beautiful woman who makes him want to settle down, but she eventually leaves him. He then meets a couple who is having problems and gives them advice, but he becomes the third party in their relationship.一个男人认为自己是个花花公子。他和一个美丽的女人约会，这个女人让他想安定下来，但她最终离开了他。然后，他遇到了一对有问题的夫妇，并向他们提供建议，但他成为了他们关系中的第三方。
